#

Zucchini Noodles with Pesto

15 min
$8.5
300 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

DairyNuts

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeVegetarianLow-Carb

Cuisine:

Italian

Course:

Main Dish

Tags:

QuickHealthyLight Meal

Description

A light and refreshing dish featuring spiralized zucchini tossed in a vibrant pesto sauce, perfect for a healthy meal.

Ingredients

  • zucchini: 2 medium
  • pesto sauce: 1 cup
  • cherry tomatoes: 1 cup
  • parmesan cheese: 1/4 cup
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
